## Tournament

- Current: "Greenbrook Singles World Championships 2026" (`singles-championship-2026`)
- Format: Round-robin, best of 3 sets, 11 players, 55 matches across 11 weeks
- $40 entry ($30 fee + $10 no-show buffer). Winner gets 80% of pot, last place gets 20%

## Lineup Optimizer

`src/lib/lineup-optimizer.ts` — greedy constraint solver considering:
- ELO ratings (strongest on highest lines)
- `doubles_only` preference (avoid singles unless necessary to prevent forfeit)
- Availability (RSVP yes/maybe)
- Minimum match fairness (boost players below 3-match goal)
- Reliability score (carrot system)
- Default-win boost (prioritize real playing time for those who won by forfeit)

## ELO System

`src/lib/elo.ts` — separate singles/doubles ratings, K-factor adjusted.
Batch recalculate via `/api/admin/elo/recalculate`. Updated live on score submission.

## TennisRecord Integration

`src/lib/tennisrecord.ts` — scrapes tennisrecord.com for player ratings, stats, match history.
`src/lib/tr-scouting.ts` — caching/persistence layer with 7-day staleness check.

- Production app fetches tennisrecord.com directly (no proxy needed)
- `tennisrecord-proxy` worker is dev-only (local WiFi blocks the site)
- Deep scout: team page → each player's profile + stats + match history (3 concurrent players)
- Data cached in `tr_players` and `tr_match_history` tables
- Own team's TR ratings synced to `players.tennisrecord_rating`
- Managed via `/admin/scouting` page or `/api/debug` `tr-backfill` action
- Cron auto-scouts: quick-scout completed opponents, deep-scout one upcoming opponent, refresh own team weekly

## AI Features

All use GPT-4o-mini. Cost: well under $1/month total.

| Feature | Library | Trigger | Est. Cost |
|---------|---------|---------|-----------|
| Pre-match hype email | `league-commentary.ts` | Cron (day before match) | ~$0.002/email |
| Post-match recap email | `league-commentary.ts` | Cron (after scores synced) | ~$0.002/email |
| Player form summaries | `player-form.ts` | Score submission + cron | ~$0.0003/call |
| Match predictions/quips | `match-predictions.ts` | Score submission + weekly digest | ~$0.008/full regen |
| Weekly digest narrative | `tournament-digest.ts` | Cron (Sundays) | ~$0.003/digest |

Pattern: each module has its own `callGpt()` helper that reads `OPENAI_API_KEY` from CloudflareEnv. Always fire-and-forget (don't block user-facing responses).

## Match Lifecycle (League)

`open` → `needs_players` → `rsvp_closed` → `lineup_draft` → `lineup_confirmed` → `locked` → `completed`
Auto-transitions via cron. Players acknowledge lineup spots after confirmation.
